{
  "texts": [
    "YOLO V4 achieves a superior and more efficient model by incorporating and integrating new features.",
    "An important theme that YOLO V4 focuses on is real-time object detection using traditional neural network models.",
    "These models only require traditional GPU training, making it possible to train, test, and implement convincing object detection models.",
    "YOLO V5 is a single-stage target detection algorithm that makes the following improvements based on YOLO V4.",
    "The model training phase introduces Mosaic data augmentation and adaptive anchor frame calculation."
  ]
}